reviewText: It features a Japanese space hero; new version of Ultraman. Too bad there were only a few episodes made; in order to make room for the next Ultraman in the next generation.

I ordered this item and the vol 2 as a present.  The ship dates provided a very broad range for delivery date, but it arrived in time to be given as a Christmas present.  The item was in the condition as advertised.  I can't comment on the quality of the discs/etc. since they were given as a gift, but will update if there are any problems.  Overall, a very quick and satisfying transaction.

This was a gift for my boyfriend, along with the other three volumes of the series. This is the most expensive of all Utraman Tiga volumes due to the fact that it was very under-produced. The other volumes are much cheaper, and this site is the cheapest way to buy this volume to date. Try searching elsewhere for the other three, you can find them for fairly cheap prices.
